HEADWORD: butene
<hw>butene</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>any of three isomeric singly
unsaturated hydrocarbons <chform>C4H8</chform>; all are used in making
synthetic rubbers; -- called also <altname>butylene</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
